            "body": "Sorry to budge in. Just giving some info for maintainers and anybody that might stumble upon this on google.\n\nThis build error happens because Void Linux [still uses](https://github.com/void-linux/void-packages/issues/38584) a musl version prior to 1.2.3, which is the version that [adds `pthread_getname_np`](https://git.musl-libc.org/cgit/musl/commit/?h=v1.2.3&id=7a43f6fea9081bdd53d8a11cef9e9fab0348c53d). Though it was being worked on at void-linux/xbps#331, it seems abandoned for several years by now.",
